{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, we were-- we were so in debt, trying for weeks-- almost nine weeks, it took us, but when we started to have the-- the feeling that we are being sort like taken into the middle of Russia was when we crossed the Ural Mountains because this is when we realized.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And anyway, one day, they dropped us in the middle of nowhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian guards.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian police, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russian guards.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, we were not beaten.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were just not on the-- not on the trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on, there were unpleasant incidents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but we were taken to a spot, which was completely middle of nowhere, really.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The middle of nowhere because it was far away from a city, far away from a township, far away from everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, we were told that do-- whatever they were-- the huts belonged to political prisoners, and they-- so they made a meeting.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said, this is where you're going to be, and this is-- they said it in Russian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can tell you Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said [NON-ENGLISH], which means, you'll get used to it, and if you will not get used to it, you will die, but die-- not in a nice way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, this is a very unpleasant Russian way of dying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was bitterly cold, and two people from every family, he's-- he said the person in charge-- which was a KGB man, which we had a lot of problems later on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said every family has to have two people in order to get a food ration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But since my mother was always sort of person that couldn't work, and she wasn't well, I was the oldest one, so I was told to go to work.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
